Development steps
-----------------
1.create spring strater project -select maven

2.set up dependency
   change the scope of msql-server to 7.4.1 in POM.xml
             
3.aplication.properties
   #server.port
   #Database authentication
   #Jpa Hybernate
4.create packages:
com.nissan.model
com.nissan.repo
com.nissan.service
